<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-white">
  <div class="container-width">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="about-content">
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">
          Why Industry Leaders Choose Endeavor
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          For over a decade, Endeavor Agency has been the trusted partner for executives who demand excellence. Our team of seasoned professionals understands the unique challenges of executive leadership.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We don't just manage tasks—we anticipate needs, solve problems proactively, and create systems that multiply your effectiveness. When you partner with Endeavor, you gain more than support; you gain a competitive advantage.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">98%</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Client retention rate</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">24/5</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Global availability</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">10+</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Years of excellence</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">500+</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Executives served</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-3xl p-12 lg:p-16">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl p-8">
            <blockquote class="text-lg text-gray-700 italic leading-relaxed">
              "Endeavor Agency transformed how I manage my time and priorities. Their team's professionalism and attention to detail is unmatched. They're not just assistants—they're strategic partners."
            </blockquote>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Sarah Chen</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">CEO, Fortune 500 Company</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-content,
  .about-image {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .about-image {
    animation-delay: 0.3s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
</style>